headline.main: Barty Wins in Malaysia for 1st Title
headline.print_headline: Barty Wins in Malaysia for 1st Title

lead_paragraph: Ashleigh Barty won her first WTA singles title after overpowering Nao Hibino 6-3, 6-2 Sunday in the Malaysian Open final.
